name: foodPantryCAT
description: Any folder in this directory that includes an `index.html` file will be part of the website. The HTML files can then link to `../css/out/index.css` for styles and the respective JavaScript file for logic.\ Common attributes of the HTML files include:\ `<meta charset="UTF-8">` for consistancy\ `<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">` for resizing\ `<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/out/index.css">` for styles
